---
title: Mint & Sweet Onion Lamb Shoulder with Cauliflower Gratin, Lemon Potatoes & Garlicky Greens
description: For tonight’s dinner, we’ve done the hard bit for you by slow cooking this lamb shoulder to meltingly tender perfection using the
famous ‘sous vide’ technique. Finished off in the oven for a crisp and golden-brown coating, then paired with a moreish mint and
onion chutney sauce, we just know you’ll love this one!
